Intelligent Display Unit integrates metro data recording and train system management, and running software that can generate the graphics based on analyze of incoming onboard equipment data.The art of state of onboard Intelligent Display Unit for metro train is introduced. The train communication network based on the Intelligent Display Unit is described. The hardware and software of the Intelligent Display Unit are designed in this paper. The EMC, Vibration and Shock type testing shown that the Intelligent Display Unit is reliable in any operating condition, and it also can operate in a variety of locomotive and public mass transit transportation modes.